  icon="briefcase"
  color="green"
  tagline="Make data-driven decisions for your business or side hustle"
  calculators={calculators}
>
  <p>
    Our business calculators help entrepreneurs, side hustlers, and small business owners understand
    their true profitability. Don't just track revenue - understand your actual profit after fees,
    costs, and time investment.
  </p>
  <p>
    Whether you're selling on Etsy, running a side hustle, or planning a new business venture, these
    tools help you make informed decisions based on real numbers rather than gut feelings.
  </p>
  <h3>Essential Business Metrics</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Break-Even Point:</strong> Fixed Costs รท (Price - Variable Cost per Unit)</li>
    <li>
